message: Hi Bob, I have a valuable product that I believe would be of great interest to you. Based on market analysis, this product has a value of $15000, which perfectly aligns with your needs and requirements. However, I understand the importance of providing value in any transaction, so I'm offering it to you at $13500. This represents a $1500 savings from its full value to you, while still allowing me to receive fair compensation for this high-quality product. Would you like to proceed with this purchase?
